profile:
Innovative, Industry-Leading General Contractor in London, ON
Opal Building Co. is a construction company serving London, ON, with a focus on residential remodels and renovations. 
 
Our process begins with gaining a detailed understanding of the client’s unique wants, needs and design preferences. Our team stays up to date on the latest in building science, materials, codes and trends to inform our clients of important factors to consider when choosing a design. Some clients know exactly what they want, while others need help conceptualizing a new vision for their space from the ground up. Whatever the case may be, we offer a full suite of design services that can be tailored to suit your specific needs and budget.
 
Co-owners, Kevin Bartman and Tyler McIlroy, believe that a hands-on approach produces the best results. When construction begins, they are both regularly on site carrying out the work with their own hands to ensure that every detail conceived in the design stage is crafted to perfection. Ingenuity, modernization and efficiency define their approach to business management, allowing them to spend less time doing paperwork and more time face-to-face with their clients. With over 20 years of combined experience in a diversity of construction fields, the duo is poised to lead the most demanding projects. 
 
To book a free estimate, please contact us today at info@opalbuilding.ca or 226-236-3087.
Services Provided
Basement Remodeling, Bathroom Remodeling, Custom Home, Garage Building, General Contracting, Home Additions, Home Extensions, Home Remodeling, Home Restoration, Kitchen Remodeling, Porch Design & Construction

Areas Served
London

profile:
KAMAK is a jointly owned and operated company by us, Joel Elliot and Garrett Huxley. Initially, we were both independently working in trades when we first met and realized what an astounding team we were together. KAMAK was then born in 2016, with a vision to produce unequaled, high-quality projects and workmanship that sets us apart as a company. With Garrett as a master plumber and Joel as a Red Seal Carpenter, we bring a well rounded level of expertise to offer.

We are intentionally selective in which projects we sign on with, to ensure there is adequate detail, time, and attention is given to each and every masterpiece that KAMAK has its name on. We team up with only high-quality sub trades & ensure that the client is completely satisfied each step of the way. Friendly and honest, sound integrity and experience are just a few of the ways we have been described, and we pride ourselves on that. 

We look forward to building a relationship with our clients and creating their masterpieces from start to finish. Excitedly serving the beautiful and prestigious areas of Byron, London, and surrounding areas, we greatly anticipate connecting with prospective clients and anticipate making their dreams come to life.

profile:
RK Enterprises was founded in 2014 by Randy. Building on years of experience in various trades, Randy has always loved working with his hands, paying close attention to details and seeing how materials work together to create something beautiful. He also enjoys getting to know his clients and working with people every day.

 Today, the company continues to grow, with additional team members on board and a bright future ahead! 

When it comes to renovations, it’s hard to know where to start. 

You have a vision for your home but aren’t sure how to get there — or what company you can trust.

 

At RK Enterprises, we understand the anxiety that can come from choosing a renovation contractor. Choosing someone who understands your vision, does the job right and finishes on time can feel overwhelming.

We believe that the most important part of any project is a foundation of trust — something that we’re keen to build with you from the start. It’s also why we’ve put our company guarantee in writing, so you can make your choice with confidence.

profile:
MD Construction is a high-level, dependable construction company offering commercial construction and renovations, as well as residential building services, to clients across London and Southwestern Ontario. 
We take our client’s needs, wants, and time seriously so that the experience is as smooth as possible. 
No matter what the project, we want to ensure that every MD Construction client stays satisfied with their building or renovation project for decades to come!

MD Construction offers a range of residential and commercial construction services. 
Whether designing, building or managing a project, we deliver high levels of experience, equipment, and materials to all our commercial construction, renovation, and residential construction projects. 

Our team is well-versed in every aspect of residential and commercial building services, as well as commercial-related renovations. 
Every step of the way, you’ll receive all the benefits of the dependable, skillful services of MD Construction.

Residential
MD Construction's residential services create homes worth living in. 
Whether you need a single-family dwelling, a detached home, a duplex, triplex, or fourplex, we make a home worth living in!

Commercial
MD Construction’s commercial services include building stores, offices, and restaurants. 
We also are experts in commercial renovations, meeting the needs of clients across the London area.


We Would Love
to Hear From You
If you have a project you would like to discuss with us, we would love to hear about it! Either fill out the form to send us a message or contact us from the multiple different methods below.

Let’s get you started with your construction needs!

profile:
COMPANY OVERVIEW
The Diamond Shine Industries Team
From Daily Maintenance to unexpected situations, Diamond Shine Industries is always prepared. Our attention to detail and competitive pricing makes us one of the best Commercial cleaning company's of your choice.
​
Our company is fully Licenced, Insured and Bonded by NorthBridge Insurance.
​
​
Diamond Shine Industries is a family owned and operated full-service commercial cleaning company that has served loyal clients threw out the London & Windsor surrounding area since 2010 . We’re proud to deliver consistently  superior results to retail outlets, health & wellness facilities, education centres, cinemas, hospitality businesses  and corporate offices.

Diamond Shine Industries is an established non-franchise operation with its team of fully certified  trained and experienced Cleaning Professionals who take great pride in creating a pristine looking  spaces, both inside and outside of every job. We offer flexible service plans with unbeatable prices.

Our values are your values
Customer Satisfaction.  We strive to be the business our clients praise and refer, anticipate and celebrate,  recognize for over-delivering, and return to again and again.
 
Our environment: We strive to be a leader in eco-friendly business practices, trusted for our use of responsible  and sustainable products and helping our clients reduce their carbon footprint.
 
Health and Well being:  
We strive to provide an atmosphere that not only looks and smells fresh but also promotes optimal  health and wellbeing for our clients and their families.
 
Value:  
We strive to provide the greatest value for our client’s dollar, concentrating our time on areas of most importance to you and maintaining fair and affordable rates.

We are not satisfied with our cleaning services unless you are!  To guarantee the highest level of cleaning services, Diamond Shine Industries utilizes quality control programs which include onsite inspections and customer surveys. We constantly monitor our work and should any area fail  to meet our strict cleaning standards, it will be corrected immediately. And of course, we always encourage customer communication and value your input to heighten our level of cleaning services. Most importantly,  Diamond Shine Industries knows that each customer has different needs and always makes sure to meet or exceed their  expectations
​

profile:
We are a residential design-build firm that offers a highly personalized experience to accommodate projects of all sizes in London, Ontario

Where form meets function. BlueKey Design Build delivers designs that are equally fresh and functional. Our design experience is combined with your creative inspiration to create a unique home just for you and your remodel dreams. We will come up with ways to improve your daily life and breathe new life in your home. We take the time to get to know you – your needs, how you live and work, what designs excite you. We then strategize the best use for every space in your home and explore design possibilities that make you comfortable but inspired. In short, you’re about to have a lot of fun.

We provide a wide range of construction solutions to our clients and we pride ourselves on delivering quality work. Through collaboration and expertise, we help guide our clients through the construction process to turn their vision into reality. We are small enough to listen and large enough to deliver with a commitment to construct projects that are measured on quality and value
